---
// CAPCS Core Ingredient: Science meets beauty
---

<section id="science" class="section science">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="science-header reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-accent-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2 class="science-title">专研贻贝钙肽CAPCS<sup>®</sup></h2>
      <p class="science-subtitle">
        <span class="science-subtitle-line">海得宝核心成分是自主研发的贻贝钙肽CAPCS®</span>
        <span class="science-subtitle-line">它提取自纯净海域的珍稀贻贝，通过纯物理回流反渗技术而成，不含任何化学溶剂残留</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="science-image-wrap reveal reveal-rise">
      <img src="/assets/capcs-ingredient.png" alt="CAPCS® 钙离子舒缓技术成分示意" class="science-image" />
    </div>

    <div class="science-points reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">30 秒快速止痒</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">临床验证止痒速度优于弱效激素（氢化可的松），效果等同于弱效激素。切断"搔抓恶性循环"，从根源缓解皮肤问题。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">13 年自主研发</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">由生物学博士后团队研发，纯物理回流反渗技术萃取。发表于《中华皮肤科杂志》与 SCI 期刊，机理与临床双重验证。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">五维金标准安全</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">无激素、无抗生素、无防腐剂。经口无毒、入眼无刺激、人体斑贴无刺激、多次皮肤刺激无刺激、4000+ 争议成分不添加。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="science-data reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">79%</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">止痒有效率</span>
      </div>
      <div class="science-data-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">67%</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">特应性皮炎治疗有效率</span>
      </div>
      <div class="science-data-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">6×</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">提高激素有效率</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .science {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-top: var(--space-6xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6xl);
  }

  .science-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-accent-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-brand);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
  }

  .science-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .science-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
  }

  .science-subtitle-line {
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Centered image ── */
  .science-image-wrap {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-image {
    display: block;
    width: 380px;
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* ── 编辑式要点列表（居中限宽，序号引导，整条 hairline 分隔）── */
  .science-points {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .science-point + .science-point {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .science-point-num {
    flex: none;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    font-size: 0;
    background: url('/assets/list-marker.png') center / contain no-repeat;
    margin-top: 0.2em;
  }

  .science-point-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .science-point-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* ── Data bar ── */
  .science-data {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .science-data-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .science-data-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-brand-dark);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .science-data-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 20ch;
  }

  .science-data-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .science-image {
      width: 280px;
    }
    .science-points {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }
    .science-point {
      gap: var(--space-md);
      padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    }
    .science-point-num {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }
    .science-data {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .science-data-divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 1px;
    }
  }
</style>
